  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strategic Assistance for Emergency Response in DRC (SAFER) Programme</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Working in eastern DRC, the project will provide multipurpose cash assistance to the most vulnerable IDPs and host families to strengthen their purchasing power, as well as NFIs to enable them to meet their basic needs; and WaSH assistance to improve their access to safe drinking water and sanitation. These response packages will have gender and protection activities mainstreamed, with gender- and protection- targeted activities addressing specific identified needs.</narrative>
  </description>
